title: 198.001 DEFINITIONS.
text:
For the purposes of this chapter, the terms defined in this section have the meanings given them.
"Resident" means a person admitted to any of the Minnesota veterans homes.
[Repealed, 1975 c 61 s 26]
"Administrator" means an administrator of any of the Minnesota veterans homes.
"Commissioner" means the commissioner of veterans affairs.
[Repealed, 2008 c 297 art 2 s 30]
[Repealed, 2004 c 219 s 7]
"Home" means any of the Minnesota veterans homes.
[Repealed, 2008 c 297 art 2 s 30]
